<Default title="Recursive Verification-Surface Collapse · Harshith Kantamneni" description="Notes from 100+ cycles of running an autonomous AI lab on a single MacBook. The null-set principal problem and three structural fixes." current="reports">

  <div class="page-grid">
    <div class="full-bleed" style="padding: var(--space-7) var(--space-4) var(--space-3); max-width: var(--grid-max); margin: 0 auto;">
